# Dual-Loop Agent Execution
## Pi-Mono Core Execution Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant AG as Agent Runtime
    participant CTX as Context Engine
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant TOOL as Tool Executor
    participant STORE as Session Store

    %% OUTER LOOP START
    Note over AG,LLM: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>⭕ OUTER LOOP START<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

    GW->>AG: dispatch(message, sessionKey)
    AG->>CTX: assemble(sessionKey, newMessage)
    CTX-->>AG: context (tokens: X,XXX)
    AG->>LLM: stream(context, tools=[...])

    LLM-->>AG: AssistantMessage (streaming chunks)
    AG-->>GW: Forward stream (user sees typing)

    LLM-->>AG: done (stream complete)

    AG->>AG: Parse tool calls from assistant message

    alt Has tool calls
        Note over AG,TOOL: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>🔧 INNER LOOP START<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

        loop Execute each tool sequentially
            AG->>TOOL: execute(tool_i, params_i)
            TOOL-->>AG: ToolResultMessage

            AG->>LLM: Continue with tool result

            LLM-->>AG: Next chunk (text OR next tool call)

            AG->>AG: Check steering messages (user intervention?)
            alt Steering detected (user said "stop")
                AG->>AG: Skip remaining tools (break inner loop)
            else No steering
                continue loop
            end
        end

        Note over AG,TOOL: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>🔚 INNER LOOP END<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
    end

    AG->>AG: Check follow-up queue (pending messages)
    alt Follow-up exists
        AG->>AG: Process next (back to outer loop start)
    else No follow-up
        AG->>CTX: ingest(final turn)
        CTX->>STORE: Persist to JSONL
        CTX->>CTX: Maybe compaction if budget exceeded

        AG-->>GW: Final response
    end

    Note over AG,LLM: ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>⭕ OUTER LOOP END<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
```

**Key Concepts:**

1. **Outer Loop** (vòng ngoài):
   - Chạy một "turn" hoàn chỉnh (user message → agent response)
   - Sau khi turn xong, check follow-up queue (tin nhắn bổ sung đang chờ)
   - Nếu có follow-up → chạy lại outer loop

2. **Inner Loop** (vòng trong):
   - Chạy khi LLM gọi tool calls
   - Thực thi từng tool một, theo thứ tự
   - Sau mỗi tool, check "steering messages" (user có thể can thiệp giữa chừng)
   - Nếu steering detected → bỏ qua tools còn lại

3. **Steering** (lǎi đà/điều khiển):
   - User có thể gửi tin nhắn mới trong khi agent đang chạy
   - Ví dụ: Agent đang đọc 100 files, user nói "Dừng lại, đọc file khác"
   - Agent nhận steering → dừng tools đang chạy, ưu tiên user message mới

4. **Follow-up** (bổ sung):
   - Các tin nhắn khác đang chờ trong queue (từ same user)
   - Khi agent free, tự động lấy follow-up tiếp
   - Tránh user phải đợi hoàn toàn mới gửi tin tiếp

**Example Timeline:**

```
T=0ms   User: "Tính tổng 100 số"
T=100ms Agent: Gọi LLM
T=500ms LLM: "Tôi cần dùng Python để tính"
T=600ms Tool: run_python("sum(range(100))"
T=700ms Tool: returns 4950
T=800ms LLM: "Tổng là 4950"
T=900ms Agent: ✅ Reply to user

(Meanwhile, at T=400ms user sent follow-up)
T=400ms User: "Nhân với 2"
T=900ms Agent: (finishes first turn)
T=901ms Agent: Sees follow-up → Outer loop again
T=1s    Agent: "4950 × 2 = 9900"
```

